nodes.text: Krystick Moonskimmer was a male member of the Benthar's Boys gang on Draenell's Point. He became Benthar's lieutenant after Droxie defected to the Vibroblade gang. Moonskimmer later joined the Alliance to Restore the Republic when Alliance operatives convinced both gangs to unit against the Galactic Empire.
